Title: From geometric quantization to Moyal quantization
Authors: Jose M. Gracia-Bondia and Joseph C. Varilly
Comments: 7 two-column pages, RevTeX, UCR--FM--03--94
Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 36 (1995) 2691-2701
\\
  We show how the Moyal product of phase-space functions, and the Weyl
correspondence between symbols and operator kernels, may be obtained directly
using the procedures of geometric quantization, applied to the symplectic
groupoid constructed by ``doubling'' the phase space.
